These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
Pet: lizard, chinchilla, hamster
1. Pet:chinchilla is on the right of Pet:hamster##1
2. Pet:lizard is on the far right##1
3. Pet:lizard is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Pet   | hamster | chinchilla | lizard |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
Movie-Genre: satire, epic, superhero
1. Movie-Genre:epic is in an odd position##4
2. Movie-Genre:satire is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | superhero | epic |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
House: gothic-revival, art-deco, futuristic
1. House:art-deco is in an even position##4
2. House:art-deco is on the left or right of House:futuristic##3
3. House:futuristic is on the right of House:art-deco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| House   | gothic-revival | art-deco | futuristic |

 #################################
 
